tyle=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">        Data1 </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">cache</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">d2</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">);</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">//cache 创建成功了</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">        _d2 </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> cache</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">//但是对于此时的 b 对象来说，b 内部的_d2 依旧会先调用 Data1 的默认构造函数，结果发现没有默认构造函数，因此调用失败，连定义_d2 都没有办法，更别说赋值给_d2 了</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">    }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">private</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">    int</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> _a2</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">    int</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> _b2</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">    int</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> _c2</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</sp